            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "87352c06e58e_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ec57",
          "text": "Greta Thunberg and Jane Goodall at the WEF in Davos, 2019 — The Regeneration rising will need all the generations and all the people alive today come together and collaborate in redesigning the human impact on Earth. The time is NOW! Regeneration Rising! Trim-tabs Unite! (Image Source)",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "1*ZtJ948-U1oziiMKOnvvwrQ.jpeg",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "OUTSET_LEFT",
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 285,
              "href": "https://www.facebook.com/Ecological-Consciousness-567337650286414/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 273,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "87352c06e58e_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "cf62",
          "text": "Jane Goodall and Greta Thunberg have demonstrated so effectively “What you do makes a difference, and you have to decide what kind of difference you want to make.” I am coming to Brazil to make a difference together with all those wonderful people I look forward to seeing again and meeting there.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "87352c06e58e_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "975e",
          "text": "Let us make a positive difference together!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 43,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "87352c06e58e_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2c63",
          "text": "As life we are capable of creating conditions conducive to life!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 64,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "87352c06e58e_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "0e57",
          "text": "May it serve the healing of the Earth and her people!",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
